query:
INSERT INTO supplier_users (userId, supplierId, role)
SELECT u.id, s.id, 'owner'
FROM users u
CROSS JOIN suppliers s
WHERE u.email = 'supplier@test.com' 
  AND s.contactEmail = 'supplier@test.com'
  AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM supplier_users su WHERE su.userId = u.id AND su.supplierId = s.id);
